---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Team | pensionable.ai">
  <section class="hero-section bg-gradient-brand-soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Our Team</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-grey">Meet the experts behind pensionable.ai's innovative pension management solutions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-light rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/team/mark.png" alt="Mark Crump - Chief Executive Officer" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Mark Crump</h3>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-crump-5551171a/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-purple transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-purple font-medium mb-4">Chief Executive Officer</p>
              <p class="text-grey mb-4">With over 20 years of experience as either CEO or CTO at Pensions Administration Software companies, Mark specialises in product design and development, while fostering lasting client relationships. His expertise lies in transforming complex problems and ideas into enterprise-grade solutions for the pensions industry.</p>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Artificial Intelligence</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Pension Systems</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Enterprise Strategy</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-light rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/team/spencer.png" alt="Spencer Lynch - Commercial Director" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Spencer Lynch</h3>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/spencelynch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-purple transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-purple font-medium mb-4">Commercial Director</p>
              <p class="text-grey mb-4">Spencer is a senior technology leader in the pensions industry, specialising in creating, developing and taking to market innovative data and technology solutions. He has a proven track record of streamlining pension administration processes to simplify the de-risking journey. Spencer is passionate about delivering solutions that make pension management more accessible, efficient and stress-free for administrators, employers, and scheme members.</p>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Business Development</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Pension Systems</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Product Strategy</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-light rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/team/jason.png" alt="Jason Rogers - Chief Technology Officer" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Jason Rogers</h3>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jasonrogers27/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-purple transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-purple font-medium mb-4">Chief Technology Officer</p>
              <p class="text-grey mb-4">With 25 years in financial services and technology, Jason brings a unique blend of operational and technical expertise gained in senior leadership roles (including COO) at multiple multi-billion dollar hedge funds. He has architected enterprise-grade reconciliation solutions, transforming complex financial workflows through innovative technological implementations.</p>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Machine Learning</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Automated Reasoning</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Data Security</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-light rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/team/andrew.png" alt="Andrew Davidson - Board Advisor" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Andrew Davidson</h3>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andydavidson1974/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-purple transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-purple font-medium mb-4">Board Advisor</p>
              <p class="text-grey mb-4">Over 25 years experience as a technology entrepreneur. Andy has founded and co-founded multiple seed-stage tech companies. He has led and built teams of over 200 people, raised over £20M in finance, scaled business to over £10M in revenue and enjoyed two large 8 figure exits within his portfolio.</p>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Enterprise Strategy</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Product Strategy</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">System Architecture</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card md:col-span-2 md:max-w-[calc(50%-1rem)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-light rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/team/david.png" alt="David Rich - Chief Data Officer" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">David Rich</h3>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-rich-epmi-4465021/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-purple transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-purple font-medium mb-4">Chief Data Officer</p>
              <p class="text-grey mb-4">Over 25 years experience as a technology and data entrepreneur. Whether undertaking de-risking programmes, improving member engagement, or delivering data to the Pensions Dashboard, good data is vital to the efficient administration of pensions. David's expertise lies in the combination of his pensions experience and deep understanding of how to improve and unlock the power of data.</p>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Pensions Data</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Data Quality</span>
                  <span class="bg-gradient-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-grey">Regulatory Engagement</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="prose max-w-none text-grey">
          <p class="mb-4">At pensionable.ai, our mission is to transform pension administration through intelligent automation and AI-powered solutions. We're dedicated to bringing mathematical precision and clarity to the complex world of pension management.</p>
          <p>Our team combines deep industry expertise with cutting-edge technology to create innovative solutions that empower pension schemes, administrators, and members to make better decisions with confidence and ease.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-purple text-4xl mb-4">•</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-grey">Pushing boundaries with advanced AI and automated reasoning technology</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-purple text-4xl mb-4">•</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Precision</h3>
          <p class="text-grey">Delivering mathematical accuracy and eliminating ambiguity in pension management</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-purple text-4xl mb-4">•</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-grey">Building reliable, secure solutions for enterprise-grade pension management</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-brand text-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Join Our Team</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">We're always looking for talented individuals to help us transform pension management</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn bg-white text-navy hover:bg-white/90">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
